cture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"lc-block\"\u003e\n            \u003chr\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"lc-block text-center mt-5 mb-5\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003ch2 class=\"font-weight-bolder\"\u003eWhy Harvester?\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"row\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"col-md-4\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"lc-block text-center\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003ch3 class=\"\"\u003eSits on the shoulders of cloud native giants \u003c/h3\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp class=\"font-weight-light\"\u003eHarvester uses some of the most proven and mature open source software (OSS)\n                components to build virtualization instead of proprietary kernels that are kept hidden from view.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"col-md-4\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"lc-block text-center\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003ch3 class=\"\"\u003eLower Total Cost of Ownership (TCO)\u003c/h3\u003e\n              \u003cp class=\"font-weight-light\"\u003eAs 100% open source, Harvester is free from the costly license fees of other\n                HCI solutions. Plus, with its foundation based on existing technology such as Linux \u0026amp; kernel- based\n                virtual machines.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"col-md-4\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"lc-block text-ce